  "1760610": {
    "name": "Car Manufacture Demo",
    "steam_appid": 1760610,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/ad2152743073c7c848c0bc3baedee996.avif?t=1724759511\" width=610 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CAR MANUFACTURE DEMO</strong></h2><strong>在《Car Manufacture Demo》中，你将建造自己的20世纪初期的汽车工厂。这个游戏版本仅限于教程，在这里你将生产你的第一辆车，并学习生产和销售的基本机制。此外，还有一个挑战任务，你需要运用你的智慧来完成一个特殊的军事车辆订单。</strong><br>只需几千美元，你就有机会建造和发展自己的工厂，设计其运作的每个方面。首先建造建筑物并组织第一条生产线。雇佣员工并培训他们，以确保他们的技能水平很高。规划最佳的生产流程并开始赚钱。你需要这些钱来开发技术并研究游戏中可用的六十种汽车型号。仔细建立你的品牌声誉，成为推广和销售的大师，在哪里受欢迎度起着关键作用。永远走在竞争对手的前面。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>创建一个独特的汽车工厂。<br></li><li>建立并优化装配线以实现高效生产。<br></li><li>管理和培训多种类型的统计驱动员工。<br></li><li>推广产品并战略性地定价。<br></li><li>通过解锁新物品和机器来改进你的工厂。<br></li><li>探索创新技术并研究新车型。<br></li><li>提高工厂的知名度以吸引更多客户。<br></li><li>参加挑战以测试你的知识和实践技能。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/ecd496892e811aa56fdb0d7a53f0d71e.poster.avif?t=1724759511\" width=610 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/ecd496892e811aa56fdb0d7a53f0d71e.webm?t=1724759511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/Subtitle_01_zh-CN.png?t=1724759511\" /></span><br>20世纪初带来了新的机遇。展示你作为一名优秀领导者的素质，成为汽车工厂的负责人。汽车行业的未来掌握在你手中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/562866ca67522b9429f9a77e67ee75f0.poster.avif?t=1724759511\" width=610 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/562866ca67522b9429f9a77e67ee75f0.webm?t=1724759511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/Subtitle_02_zh-CN.png?t=1724759511\" /></span><br>发现生产线的潜力，该生产线通过降低生产成本和加快汽车装配速度而革新了汽车历史。从单个工作站开始，然后将它们组合在一起并相应地分配任务。学习如何优化整个过程并确保零件的定期供应。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/6914412bc8b0540d866a9f3cbf25a9d9.poster.avif?t=1724759511\" width=610 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/6914412bc8b0540d866a9f3cbf25a9d9.webm?t=1724759511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/Subtitle_03_zh-CN.png?t=1724759511\" /></span><br>研究部门对于工厂发现新汽车项目至关重要。每个新项目的发现都需要越来越多的经验和时间。获得新技术，以构建支持和加快科学家工作的先进设备。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/c6ff2f5cb2c42fdbde409964f2b3a392.poster.avif?t=1724759511\" width=610 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/c6ff2f5cb2c42fdbde409964f2b3a392.webm?t=1724759511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/Subtitle_04_zh-CN.png?t=1724759511\" /></span><br>每辆车的背后都是具有不同经验水平的人。确保工厂满负荷运转是你的责任。管理和培训你的员工，根据他们的技能分配任务。保持他们的满意和充足的休息以确保高效工作。然而，请记住，受过良好培训的员工要求更高的工资。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/39e0dcfbfeb8a347a422936641cef65f.poster.avif?t=1724759511\" width=610 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/39e0dcfbfeb8a347a422936641cef65f.webm?t=1724759511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/Subtitle_05_zh-CN.png?t=1724759511\" /></span><br>每辆车都有其生命周期，在此期间其受欢迎程度上升，客户愿意花更多钱。学习何时进行促销、降价或停止生产特定型号。整体趋势和制造汽车的品牌质量影响着受欢迎程度。注意这一点，因为它直接影响销售和工厂的成功。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/772da8835ccb8d6b7a00adbf49b66799.poster.avif?t=1724759511\" width=610 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/772da8835ccb8d6b7a00adbf49b66799.webm?t=1724759511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760610/extras/Subtitle_06_zh-CN.png?t=1724759511\" /></span><br>尝试游戏机制。其中一些需要多次尝试才能达到最佳效果。你的工厂可能是一个高度复杂的系统，但仅仅观察它可能也是一种非常放松的体验。随着你积累经验，你可以接受各种挑战并在短期任务中测试你的技能。有些任务很棘手，需要创造力才能获得大量星星。在我们的Discord服务器上分享你的印象。",
